OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIsraeli forces continue to commit
OL,8,Fgenocide against Palestinians by
OL,9,Fdeliberately targeting children in the
OL,10,FGaza Strip, an independent United
OL,11,FNations Commission of Inquiry has
OL,12,Ffound.
OL,14,FIn a report published on Tuesday, the
OL,15,Fcommission ` which last year concluded
OL,16,FIsrael had committed genocide in Gaza
OL,17,F` found that Israeli military
OL,18,Foperations have continued, causing
OL,19,F"unprecedented death, injury and
OL,20,Ftrauma" to Palestinian children.
OL,26,@{D@AOU|D@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
