FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe commission describes what it says
OL,8,Fis the deliberate targeting of
OL,9,Fchildren as a key indicator of Israeli
OL,10,Fauthorities' genocidal intent to
OL,11,Fdestroy the Palestinian people,
OL,12,Fincluding after the ceasefire in Gaza
OL,13,Ftook effect.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,F"Even after the October 2025
OL,8,Fceasefire, children continue to be
OL,9,Fkilled and seriously injured, with
OL,10,Fcontinued disregard by Israel for the
OL,11,Fceasefire and for the protection owed
OL,12,Fto Palestinian children under
OL,13,Finternational law," said Srinivasan
OL,14,FMuralidhar, chairman of the commission.
OL,16,FThe Israeli government has repeatedly
OL,17,Fdenied committing genocide, and
OL,18,Fofficials denounced Tuesday's UN
OL,19,Ffindings.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@SO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIsrael's Foreign Ministry called it "a
OL,8,Fpropaganda piece as outrageous as its
OL,9,Fprevious ones," while Danny Danon,
OL,10,FIsrael's ambassador to the United
OL,11,FNations, said it was a "political
OL,12,Fblood libel disguised as a UN
OL,13,Fdocument".
OL,15,F"Instead of addressing Hamas' crimes,
OL,16,Fthe October 7 massacre, the hostages,
OL,17,Fand Hamas' cynical use of children and
OL,18,Fcivilians as human shields, the
OL,19,Fcommission has once again chosen to
OL,20,Fplace Israel in the dock."
OL,26,@oD@eOUqD@OO]sD@XOUuD@IO]wD@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/12
