OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe report details conditions Israel
OL,8,Fhas imposed on Gaza since the
OL,9,Fceasefire, including widespread
OL,10,Fattacks and the blocking of
OL,11,Fhumanitarian and medical aid, which it
OL,12,Fsaid caused "multi-layered harm to
OL,13,FPalestinian children's survival,
OL,14,Fhealth and development".
OL,26,@tD@MOUvD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt documents what it describes as a
OL,8,Fsystematic pattern of Israeli attacks
OL,9,Fon hospitals, health clinics, and
OL,10,Freproductive facilities, with
OL,11,Fdevastating short and long-term
OL,12,Fconsequences for children's physical
OL,13,Fand psychological well-being.
OL,15,FThe US-backed ceasefire came into
OL,16,Feffect in October, ending two years of
OL,17,Fwar in Gaza.
OL,19,FHowever, the report noted that
OL,20,F"hostilities did not cease but rather
OL,21,Fwere reduced".
OL,26,@|D@AOU}D@MO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/12
