PN,30707
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FEight months on, Israel has carried
OL,8,Fout near-daily airstrikes, killing
OL,9,Fover 1,000 Palestinians, including
OL,10,Fover 250 children, according to the
OL,11,FPalestinian Ministry of Health.
OL,13,FIsrael has accused Hamas of repeatedly
OL,14,Fviolating the ceasefire and refusing
OL,15,Fto lay down its arms.
OL,17,FMost of Gaza's population still lives
OL,18,Fin tents, with Israel blocking
OL,19,Freconstruction materials and heavy
OL,20,Fequipment over Hamas' refusal to
OL,21,Fdisarm.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
