CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FAn international security force was
OL,8,Fsupposed to deploy to Gaza under US
OL,9,FPresident Donald Trump's peace plan,
OL,10,Fwith Israel gradually withdrawing.
OL,12,FInstead, Israel has expanded its
OL,13,Fterritorial control; Prime Minister
OL,14,FBenjamin Netanyahu has said Israel's
OL,15,Fforces now control 70% of the enclave.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
