OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe report also focused on the
OL,8,Foccupied West Bank and East Jerusalem,
OL,9,Faccusing Israel of war crimes and
OL,10,Fhighlighting "a sharp increase in
OL,11,Fviolence" against Palestinian children
OL,12,Fby Israeli settlers.
