OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FIt concluded that the Israeli military
OL,8,Fhas "repeatedly employed unreasonable,
OL,9,Fexcessive and punitive force against
OL,10,Fchildren as a tool of control,
OL,11,Fdeterrence and collective
OL,12,Fintimidation" in the West Bank.
OL,26,@pD@EOUtD@MO]
