OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1782312495
OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe Palestinian Ministry of Foreign
OL,8,FAffairs welcomed the report's
OL,9,Ffindings, saying its importance lies
OL,10,Fin "reaffirming the international
OL,11,Fcommunity's failure to stop the
OL,12,Fviolations committed by the occupying
OL,13,Fpower and to hold accountable those
OL,14,Fresponsible for these crimes against
OL,15,FPalestinian children".
OL,26,@rD@DOUwD@UO]
