OL,3,CIsrael committing genocide by
OL,4,Ctargeting children in Gaza, UN inquiry
OL,5,Cfinds
OL,7,FThe commission called on the Israeli
OL,8,Fgovernment to "immediately halt
OL,9,Fmilitary operations in Gaza," and to
OL,10,Fabide by its "special obligations
OL,11,Ftowards children under international
OL,12,Flaw".
